849. 
\fs38\fsmilli19360 WILLIAM GOULDSTONE
\fs35\fsmilli17600  (26) was indicted for, and charged on the Coroner's Inquisition with, the wilful murder of Charles Gouldstone.\cb1 \

\fs31\fsmilli15840 \cb3 MESSRS. POLAND
\fs35\fsmilli17600  
\f1\i and
\f0\i0  
\fs31\fsmilli15840 MONTAGU WILLIAMS
\fs35\fsmilli17600  
