\cf2 \cb3 the habit of visiting me\'97I married his sister\'97he would usually call on Saturday afternoon and sit in a chair and play with his hat\'97if I spoke to him he would invariably answer me the wrong question and take three or four minutes to answer me, and I would frequently remark that I thought he was very strange in his manner.\cb1 \

\f1\i \cb3 Cross-examined.
